<br>
With the great speed she had inherited from....only the gods know who,she was at the site. And what a site. She came up on the amazon side and stood near the queens.Her eyes going from each queen and she offered a lil smirk as her green eyes sparkled with lunacy. She then turned her attention to those gods who she would enjoy later on kicking thier butts.<br>
<br>
Her dark blonde hair flowed slightly in the breeze. She wore she normal attire,that of a red top and black leather pants that had now been pretty much shredded from those spikes that quite often petruded from her flesh,which not only made great weapons but also great armor in such times as war. Her face was painted,not with war paints,but blood,blood which most likely came from some poor peasant. She was even barefooted,she found it much simpler to move about without foot-wear.<br>
<br>
She licks her lips lightly before beginning to pace around the amazons. Back and forth back and forth from one side to the next side of the handful of amazons that had gathered.Her eyes darting here and there taking in her surrounding. She was excited and barely able to hold back her anticipation. <br>
<br>
&quot;Come on come on come on,someone make the first move.&quot; Her hands were flexing,and the veins in her arms visably pulsing,even her temple were pulsing as she ground her teeth in anticipation.  <p>---Everybody Got a sanity------I've got a split personality---</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenvaria.showPublicProfile?language=EN>QueenVaria</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="C:/Windows/Desktop/xenastuf/tsianina2.art" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 50<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(11/16/01 9:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7.topic&index=51>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=c:/Windows/Desktop/xenastuf/tjcontenderpremiere.art WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Zelia</span><hr size=1> Varia glanced at Zelia with wide eyes. She had never seen anyone like her before. Slowly she leaned over toward DeL and whispered, ~Who on earth is THAT?~ <p><html> <font face="Signet Roundhand ATT"> Queen Varia </font> </html></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazondelerium.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon DeLerium</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon</span><br>  Posts: 161<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(11/17/01 12:25 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7.topic&index=52>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/deleriuml9/images/del2.bmp WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Zelia</span><hr size=1> ~ DeL smirked lightly as Varia's eyes grew wide. Not everyone was used to se amazons act ad look like that, but DeL, she 