<br>
Her eyes drift once more over to Maytha,she gives her a wink before looking over to the Gods who were opposite the amazons. Her eyes stopping and fixing on Hypnos. Hmmm,another one she remembered,but had no idea why she remembered him. <br>
<br>
She then looks back to Varia. &quot;You know,I am getting a bit anxious. If you'll excuse me.&quot; With that Zelia wanders over to a weapon cart which, (lets say) someone drug to the battle site as for extra weapons. She looks over the weapons before choosing a spear. She grasps the spear in her right hand then walks to the front of the line. She takes a glance around at the others and seeing noone is prepared to give the attack signal,she takes it upon her self to get the party started.<br>
<br>
She raises the spear up. &quot; Lets do this!!!!&quot; She yells,then brings the spear back,her eyes fixing on Hypnos,just cause he looked at her the wrong way,she thrusts her arm forward,releasing the spear at a precise moment. The spear shoots through the air giving off an awful whistling sound as it flies across the field and heads directly at Hypnos,but as Zelia had planned,the spear comes short and stabs into the ground just infront of Hypnos,the spear having a motion that causes it to snap back and forth and as it snaps forward the shaft of the spear (Is Suppose to,if you take the hit,Hypnos!) wacks Hypnos in the nose.<br>
